content: प्रत्यंच्, प्रत्यच् {%<ab>a.</ab>%} (प्रतीची {%<ab>f.</ab>%} or according to <ls>Vopadeva</ls> प्रत्यंची also) {@--1@} Turned or directed towards. {@--2@} Being behind. {@--3@} Following, subsequent. {@--4@} Averted, turned sway, turning back; <ls>Pt. 3. 181.</ls> {@--5@} Western, westerly. {@--6@} Inner, interior. {@--7@} Equal to, a match for. {%--<ab>m.</ab>%} {@--1@} The individual soul. {@--2@} Future time.
